#: ../../M/management.rst:5
msgid "management"
msgstr "management"

#: ../../M/management.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../M/management.rst:10
msgid ""
"Corporate power elites distinguished primarily by their distance from actual"
" productive work and their chronic failure to manage (see also "
":ref:`suit`\\). Spoken derisively, as in \"Management decided that ...\"."
msgstr ""
"主に実際の生産的な仕事からの距離と、慢性的なマネジメントの失敗によって特徴づけられる企業の権力エリート(\\ :ref:`suit`\\ "
"も参照)。「Managementが…を決めた」のように、侮蔑的に口にされる。"

#: ../../M/management.rst:14
msgid ""
"Mythically, a vast bureaucracy responsible for all the world's minor "
"irritations. Hackers' satirical public notices are often signed ‘The Mgt’; "
"this derives from the *Illuminatus* novels (see the "
":ref:`Bibliography<bibliography>` in Appendix C)."
msgstr ""
"神話的には、世界中のあらゆる些細な苛立ちに責任を負う巨大な官僚機構。ハッカーの風刺的な公示はしばしば‘The Mgt’と署名される。これは\\ "
"*Illuminatus*\\ の小説に由来する(付録Cの\\ :ref:`参考文献<bibliography>`\\ を参照)。"
